WORKFLOW

# ⚡ AI-Powered Energy Forecasting Using Multi-Agent Systems (MAS)

This repository contains the full code, models, and documentation for our research project:  
**“AI for Energy Efficiency in Smart Grids Using Multi-Agent Systems”** – designed for scalable renewable energy forecasting and optimization.

---

## 📌 Project Objectives

- 📈 Short-term renewable energy forecasting using **LSTM** and **Prophet**
- 🧠 Anomaly detection to identify grid disturbances
- 🎯 Optimization using **Pyomo** for energy dispatch
- 🕸️ Multi-Agent collaboration: Forecasting Agent, Anomaly Agent, Optimization Agent
- 📊 Integration with Streamlit/Power BI dashboards

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

| Component        | Tools Used                         |
|------------------|------------------------------------|
| Forecasting      | LSTM, Prophet (Python)             |
| Anomaly Detection| Statistical Z-score, IsolationForest|
| Optimization     | Pyomo, Scipy                        |
| Multi-Agent Sys. | Python classes + Async execution   |
| Deployment       | Streamlit / Power BI + Flask API   |
| Dataset          | CEA, MNRE, POSOCO, IMD, NREL India |

---

